org.apache.ignite.spi.swapspace

Class SwapKey

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ignite.spi.swapspace.SwapKey

  • public class SwapKey
extends Object
    Utility wrapper class that represents swap key.

    This class also holds information about partition this key belongs to (if needed for caches).
